OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloud and rain with snow
OL,6,Faffecting highest peaks, clearing away
OL,7,Feastwards by late morning. Sunny
OL,8,Fspells developing, with blustery heavy
OL,9,Fshowers and a risk of snow on high
OL,10,Fground.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRemaining windy for most with
OL,13,Fshowers, perhaps merging to a spell of
OL,14,Frain across the Pennines. Driest
OL,15,Fweather later in the night especially
OL,16,Facross eastern areas with some clear
OL,17,Fspells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
