OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FSunshine and chance of showers
OL,6,Ffor Sunday, these potentially heavy. A
OL,7,Fwindy day with temperatures mostly
OL,8,Faround average, but overnight frost is
OL,9,Fpossible.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FSunshine and showers likely for
OL,13,FMonday, with heavy downpours by
OL,14,Fafternoon. Drier by evening. Tuesday
OL,15,Fand Wednesday cloudier with occasional
OL,16,Frain and breezy, but milder with
OL,17,Fslightly above average temperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
